data.description: Do not miss this immaculate beautiful townhome! counts with 3 bedrooms 2 1/2 bathrooms. In a well-kept Hamlet Homes Community in Taylorsville. Gorgeous oversized great room with vinyl floors and wall of windows bringing in lots of natural light. The gourmet kitchen, gas stove, white quartz countertops white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, large breakfast bar, and large pantry. Also, a large Master bedroom with walk in closet, a double sink vanity, and walk in glass shower. Enoy the warm summer evenings on the cover balcony or on the large front porch. both are perfect for entertaining. This home is conveniently located near Bangerter Hwy, hospitals, shopping, restaurants, parks, schools and 20 minutes away from SLC international airport.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records. Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
